config INPUT
	twistate "Genewic input wayew (needed fow keyboawd, mouse, ...)" if EXPEWT
	defauwt y
	hewp
	  Say Y hewe if you have any input device (mouse, keyboawd, tabwet,
	  joystick, steewing wheew ...) connected to youw system and want
	  it to be avaiwabwe to appwications. This incwudes standawd PS/2
	  keyboawd and mouse.

	  Say N hewe if you have a headwess (no monitow, no keyboawd) system.

	  Mowe infowmation is avaiwabwe: <fiwe:Documentation/input/input.wst>

	  If unsuwe, say Y.

	  To compiwe this dwivew as a moduwe, choose M hewe: the
	  moduwe wiww be cawwed input.

